MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to open the cash register.

MAIN.translated: 载具最大空中转体次数

MAIN.original: ~s~The first time you bring up the phone after receiving the message press ~INPUT_PHONE_ACCEPT~ to quick read the message, otherwise use the phone interface to access the text message.
MAIN.translated: ~s~收到短信后第一次拿出手机时，按~INPUT_PHONE_ACCEPT~可快速查看短信内容，其他情况下请从菜单中查看。

MAIN.original: ~s~The special icon above the radar is a mission replay text message. If you read this message and you select the ~h~replay~s~ option you will replay the last mission you failed.
MAIN.translated: ~s~小地图上方的特殊图标是重玩任务的短信。阅读短信并选择~h~重玩~s~后将重新开始你刚才失败的任务。

MAIN.original: To read the text message press ~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~ to bring up the phone. You can instantly read the message by pressing ~INPUT_PHONE_ACCEPT~ while the small icon is displayed.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~拿出手机阅读短信。信封图标出现时，按~INPUT_PHONE_ACCEPT~可直接阅读。

MAIN.original: To access a message any other time press ~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~, then press ~INPUT_PHONE_ACCEPT~ to access the phone menu and select 'messages'.
MAIN.translated: 其他情况下，按~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~拿出手机，然后按~INPUT_PHONE_ACCEPT~进入菜单，选择「短信」以查看短信。

MAIN.original: If you have unread messages they will be represented by an envelope icon below the radar.
MAIN.translated: 有未读短信时，小地图上方会显示信封图标。

MAIN.original: This is the best I can do with this wreck
MAIN.translated: 对这破玩意我已经尽力了

MAIN.original: The other players chose to kick you from their game.
MAIN.translated: The other players chose to kick you from their game.
还剩 ~1~ 个特技飞跃待完成。

MAIN.original: Just one stunt jump left to do.
MAIN.translated: 只剩一个特技飞跃要完成了。

MAIN.original: During the stunt camera mode use ~PAD_RSTICK_UPDOWN~ to control the slow motion speed.
MAIN.translated: 特技镜头模式下，用~PAD_RSTICK_UPDOWN~控制慢动作速度。

MAIN.original: Hold the left mouse button to grab the image and move it into place. Scroll the mouse with the right button held to scale the picture up or down. Use the buttons to stretch the picture if necessary.
MAIN.translated: 按住鼠标左键拖动图像，对其进行移动。按住右键时可用鼠标滚轮缩放图片。如有必要，可用鼠标按键拉伸图片。

MAIN.original: You have been signed out of Xbox LIVE because another person signed in using your gamer profile. Returning to single player...
MAIN.translated: 因您的账号在其他地方登录，您已从 Xbox LIVE 注销。正在返回单人模式...

MAIN.original: You have been signed out of Social Club because another person signed in using your gamer profile. Returning to single player...
MAIN.translated: 因您的账号在其他地方登录，您已从 Social Club 注销。正在返回单人模式...

MAIN.original: You have been signed out because another person signed in using your profile. Returning to single player...
MAIN.translated: 因您的账号在其他地方登录，您已注销。正在返回单人模式...

MAIN.original: You are too far away from the action, turn back or suffer the consequences.
MAIN.translated: 你离行动区域太远了，立刻调头，否则将遭受惩罚。

MAIN.original: While on this mission your cash increased by $~1~.
MAIN.translated: 在此任务中，你的金钱增加了$~1~。

MAIN.original: While on this mission your cash reduced by $~1~.
MAIN.translated: 在此任务中，你的金钱减少了by $~1~。

MAIN.original: Installing data to hard disk drive.
MAIN.translated: 正在将数据装载至硬盘驱动器。

MAIN.original: More than one gamer profile is signed in. Press any button on the desired controller to select your controller and gamer profile.
MAIN.translated: 已登录了多个账号。按下要使用的手柄上的任意按键选择需要使用的手柄及账号。

MAIN.original: Are you sure you want to reset your Display Settings to default?
MAIN.translated: 确定要将您的显示设置恢复为默认配置吗？

MAIN.original: Cheat activated ~n~Achievements "Cleaned The Mean Streets", "Finish Him", "One Man Army" and "Walk Free" blocked.
MAIN.translated: 秘籍已启用~n~成就 "Cleaned The Mean Streets" "Finish Him" "One Man Army" "Walk Free" 无法获得。

MAIN.original: Cheat activated ~n~Achievements "One Man Army" and "Walk Free" blocked.
MAIN.translated: 秘籍已启用~n~成就 "One Man Army" "Walk Free" 无法获得。

MAIN.original: Cheat activated ~n~Achievement "Cleaned The Mean Streets" blocked.
MAIN.translated: 秘籍已启用~n~成就 "Cleaned The Mean Streets" 无法获得。

MAIN.original: Cheat activated ~n~Achievements "Finish Him", "One Man Army" and "Walk Free" blocked.
MAIN.translated: 秘籍已启用~n~成就 "Finish Him" "One Man Army" "Walk Free" 无法获得。
秘籍已启用~n~成就 "Finish Him" 无法获得。
秘籍已启用~n~成就 "One Man Army" 无法获得。
秘籍已启用~n~成就 "Walk Free" 无法获得。

MAIN.original: Cheat activated ~n~This money does not count towards achievement "Half Million".
MAIN.translated: 秘籍已启用~n~这些钱不会计入成就 "Half Million" 的进度。

MAIN.original: ~s~Saving content. Please don't turn off your system.
MAIN.translated: ~s~存储内容中。~n~请不要关闭您的系统。

MAIN.original: ~s~Saving content. Please don't turn off your system.
MAIN.translated: ~s~存储内容中。~n~请不要关闭您的系统。

MAIN.original: The most recent save game appears to be damaged and cannot be loaded.
MAIN.translated: 最后保存的存档已损坏，无法读取。

MAIN.original: Slot ~1~ contains damaged save game data. Do you want to overwrite the data in this slot with your current game progress?
MAIN.translated: 栏位 ~1~ 存在损坏的存档数据。是否要用当前游戏进度覆盖该栏位的数据？

MAIN.original: The autosave slot contains damaged save game data. Do you want to overwrite the data in this slot with your current game progress?
MAIN.translated: 自动存档栏位存在损坏的存档数据。是否要用当前游戏进度覆盖该栏位的数据？

MAIN.original: Load failed. Starting a New Game...
MAIN.translated: 载入失败。正在开始新游戏...

MAIN.original: While the HDD access indicator is flashing, data is being saved. Do not switch off the power during this time.
MAIN.translated: HDD 访问指示器闪烁说明正在保存数据。请不要在此时关闭电源。

MAIN.original: Grand Theft Auto IV requires space on the hard disk drive. Please make space available.
MAIN.translated: Grand Theft Auto IV 需要更多硬盘空间。请准备更多空间。

MAIN.original: There was an error installing data to the hard disk drive.
MAIN.translated: 将数据装载至硬盘时出错。

MAIN.original: Episode ~e~ has been downloaded. ~n~Do you want to play it?
MAIN.translated: Episode ~e~ 已下载。~n~是否要进行游玩？

MAIN.original: The current network game requires downloadable content that was unavailable. Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~ to return to single player.
MAIN.translated: 当前联网游戏所需的 DLC 不可用。按~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~返回单人模式。

MAIN.original: FOR BEST EXPERIENCE, ADJUST THE SETTINGS UNTIL THE DARKEST GRAY IS JUST VISIBLE
MAIN.translated: 为了最佳游戏体验，调整以上设置，直到最深的灰色恰好可见。

MAIN.original: FOR BEST EXPERIENCE, ADJUST THE SETTINGS UNTIL THE LIGHTEST GRAY IS JUST VISIBLE
MAIN.translated: 为了最佳游戏体验，调整以上设置，直到最浅的灰色恰好可见。

MAIN.original: You need an extra ~1~KB to save into this slot. Try overwriting an existing save game in another slot or quit the game and free the required space.
MAIN.translated: 还需要 ~1~KB 空间才能保存到此栏位。请覆盖其他栏位的已有存档，或退出游戏空出所需空间。

MAIN.original: The storage device that active downloadable content is stored on has been removed. Please replace the storage device.
MAIN.translated: 存储激活的 DLC 内容的存储设备已移除。请放回此存储设备。

MAIN.original: The downloadable content you require is not available. Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~ to return to Grand Theft Auto IV.
MAIN.translated: 您请求的 DLC 暂不可用。按~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~返回 Grand Theft Auto IV。

MAIN.original: You need an extra ~1~KB of hard disk drive space for save game data. Please quit the game and free space on your hard disk drive.
MAIN.translated: 还需要 ~1~KB 硬盘空间才能保存当前进度。请退出游戏，在硬盘中空出所需空间。

MAIN.original: ~s~Loading content. Please don't turn off your console.
MAIN.translated: ~s~载入内容中。~n~请不要关闭您的主机。

MAIN.original: ~s~Loading content. Please don't turn off your system.
MAIN.translated: ~s~载入内容中。~n~请不要关闭您的系统。

MAIN.original: ~s~Loading content. Please don't turn off your system.
MAIN.translated: ~s~载入内容中。~n~请不要关闭您的系统。

MAIN.original: This game saves data automatically at certain points. Do not switch off the power when the HDD access indicator is flashing.
MAIN.translated: 本游戏会在特定时刻自动存储数据。请不要在 HDD 访问指示器闪烁时关闭电源。

MAIN.translated: 硬盘中不存在已保存的游戏进度。

MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to pick up this weapon. It will replace any weapon you have of the same type.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_PICKUP~拾起此武器。它将会替换你现有的同类武器。

MAIN.original: The installed game is corrupted. The game will close. You must delete the installed game and then reinstall it to play this game.

MAIN.translated: 需要「夜生活之曲」 DLC 才能加入这一多人战局。

MAIN.translated: ~e~ 已下载。~n~是否要进行游玩？

MAIN.translated: 正在保存视频。~n~请不要关闭您的系统。

MAIN.original: Favorite activity with Armando and Henrique
MAIN.translated: 最喜爱与Armando及Henrique进行的活动

MAIN.original: You cannot edit videos because you have insufficient memory.
MAIN.translated: 您的内存不足，无法编辑视频。

MAIN.original: Storyboard: Drag clips here to create your Video.
MAIN.translated: Storyboard：将片段拖到此处以创建视频。

MAIN.original: Clip Timeline:__Displays Clips relative to the Video length.
MAIN.translated: 片段时间轴：__显示片段相对于视频的长度。

MAIN.original: Audio Timeline:__Drag a song here to add music to your Video.
MAIN.translated: 音频时间轴：__将歌曲拖到此处可为视频添加音乐。

MAIN.original: Text Timeline:__Drag a text box here to add titles to your Video.
MAIN.translated: 文本时间轴：__将文本框拖到此处可为视频添加字幕。

MAIN.original: Text Timeline:__Drag a text box here to add titles to your Video.
MAIN.translated: 文本时间轴：__将文本框拖到此处可为视频添加字幕。

MAIN.original: Please wait while your Video is being exported.
MAIN.translated: 导出视频时请耐心等待。

MAIN.original: Clips can be dragged into the Favorites folder and will be marked with a star. Deleting clips from Favorites will not delete them from their original folders.
MAIN.translated: 拖入收藏夹的片段会用星星标记。删除收藏夹中的片段并不会删除原文件夹中的片段。

MAIN.original: Folders organize clips into categories. Click a folder to expand it.
MAIN.translated: 根据录制时间将片段归类到了不同的文件夹。点击文件夹可显示其中的内容。

MAIN.original: To add a clip to the video, drag it onto the Storyboard. Multiple instances of the same clip can exist in a given video.
MAIN.translated: 将片段拖动至Storyboard即可将其加入视频。同一片段可在视频中多次使用。

MAIN.original: To enter text, double click on the text box. To change the text settings click the Font, Size, Color and Duration values. To add text to the video, drag it onto the Text Timeline.
MAIN.translated: 双击文本框以输入文本。点击字体、大小、颜色与持续时间可修改文本样式。将文本拖入文本时间轴可将其插入视频。

MAIN.original: TIME BAR EXTENTS: Drag time bar extents to trim clip length.
MAIN.translated: 截取范围：拖动滑块可调整剪辑长度。

MAIN.original: TIMER: Toggles between Clip time and Video Time when clicked.
MAIN.translated: 计时器：点击时会在片段时间与视频时间之间切换。

MAIN.original: PLACE MARKER: Click to place a marker at the current frame.
MAIN.translated: 放置标记：在当前帧放置标记。

MAIN.original: PREVIOUS MARKER: Click to select previous marker.
MAIN.translated: 上一标记：选中上一个标记。

MAIN.original: NEXT MARKER: Click to select next marker.
MAIN.translated: 下一标记：选中下一个标记。

MAIN.original: TOOLS: Click to open the tools menu.
SAVE: Click to save clip edits.
MAIN.translated: 保存：保存对片段的编辑。

MAIN.original: Marker Controls are applied to a clip from one marker to the next.
MAIN.translated: 「标记」中的设定会作用到下一个标记前。

MAIN.original: Apply various filters to the clip by clicking on the presets, or by using the mouse wheel to quick scan.
MAIN.translated: 点击切换滤镜，亦可通过鼠标滚轮快速浏览所有预设。

MAIN.original: Filter controls alter the appearance of the clip from the current marker. Applying Filters will affect all subsequent markers if their Filters are set to none.
MAIN.translated: 「滤镜」可以改变当前标记后的画面。若之后的标记没有滤镜，应用滤镜将会影响之后的所有标记。

MAIN.original: Camera controls allow various cameras and behaviors to be placed within a clip from the current marker.
MAIN.translated: 「相机」可对当前标记处的镜头进行设置，存在多种相机与运镜选项。

MAIN.original: Alter the playback speed by clicking the presets, or by using the mouse wheel to quick scan. The Time Bar will adjust as it recalculates the length of the clip.
MAIN.translated: 点击改变播放速度，亦可通过鼠标滚轮快速浏览所有预设。虽然改变了剪辑时长，但时间轴会自动调整。

MAIN.original: Alter sound effect, music volume, and speech settings by clicking the presets, or by using the mouse wheel to quick scan.
MAIN.translated: 点击改变音效、音乐音量，开关对白，亦可通过鼠标滚轮快速浏览所有预设。

MAIN.original: Audio controls alter the sound effect, music and speech volumes of the clip from the current marker. Global Audio settings can be applied in the tools menu.
MAIN.translated: 「音频」可以改变当前标记之后的音效、音乐与对白的音量。可在工具栏内对音频进行全局调整。

MAIN.original: Speed controls alter the playback rate of the clip from the current marker.
MAIN.translated: 「速度」可以改变当前标记之后的片段的播放速率。

MAIN.original: Allows you select preset or custom cameras. Only Custom cameras can be altered.
MAIN.translated: 可以选择预设相机或自定义相机。能被调整的只有自定义相机。

MAIN.original: Allows you to select preset camera views.
MAIN.translated: 可以选择预设相机的视点。

MAIN.original: Allows you to select target or free camera views.
MAIN.translated: 可以选择目标相机或自由相机。

MAIN.original: The default target is the Player. Cycle targets by clicking or by using the mouse wheel to quick scan.
MAIN.translated: 默认目标为玩家。点击切换目标，亦可通过鼠标滚轮快速浏览。

MAIN.original: The target camera's horizontal and vertical position can be locked relative to the target.
MAIN.translated: 可以相对于目标锁定相机的水平与垂直位置。

MAIN.original: Locks the horizontal position of the camera relative to the target.
MAIN.translated: 相对于目标锁定相机的水平位置。

MAIN.original: Locks the horizontal and vertical position of the camera relative to the target.
MAIN.translated: 相对于目标锁定相机的水平与垂直位置。

MAIN.original: The target camera can be placed in an orbit around a target. Any character within range of the player's character is a valid target.
MAIN.translated: 目标相机可被放置在环绕某目标的轨道上。处在玩家角色范围内的任何角色都是合法目标。

MAIN.original: The free camera allows you to place a static camera wherever you like, within range of your character.
MAIN.translated: 自由相机允许您在玩家角色范围内的任意位置放置一个静止的相机。

MAIN.original: Alters the Field Of View (FOV) of the camera.
Applies camera movement which will transition to the next marker.
MAIN.translated: 启用后相机会平滑运动到下一标记的相机位置。

MAIN.original: Applies varying levels of camera shake to mimic a handheld camera.
MAIN.translated: 可以通过不同的晃动程度模拟手持相机拍摄。

MAIN.original: An Orbit movement travels in an arc around the target between marker positions.
MAIN.translated: 轨道运动会以环绕目标的圆周轨迹在标记位置间移动。

MAIN.original: A Linear movement travels in a straight line between marker positions.
MAIN.translated: 线性运动会以直线在两个标记位置间移动。

MAIN.original: A Blend movement allows for smooth camera movement between three or more marker positions.
MAIN.translated: 混合运动可实现相机在三个及以上的标记位置间平滑移动。

MAIN.original: Camera movement into and out of the marker can be modified by applying ease.
MAIN.translated: 缓动可以改变靠近/远离标记时相机的移动速度。

MAIN.original: Camera movement into the marker will be slowed.
MAIN.translated: 靠近标记时相机先快后慢。

MAIN.original: Camera movement out of the marker will be slowed.
MAIN.translated: 远离标记时相机先慢后快。

MAIN.original: Camera movement into and out of the marker will be slowed.
MAIN.translated: 靠近标记时相机先快后慢，远离标记时相机先慢后快。

MAIN.original: TOOLS: Click to open the tools menu.
MAIN.translated: 工具栏：点击打开工具菜单。

MAIN.original: Double click to launch the Video Editor where you can combine clips, music, text and transitions to create videos.
MAIN.translated: 双击启动视频编辑器，您可以借此组合片段、音乐、文本与转场来创建视频。

MAIN.original: Songs can be previewed by highlighting a song and pressing the play button. To add a song to the video, drag it onto the Audio Timeline.
MAIN.translated: 选中歌曲后按下播放键可试听歌曲。将歌曲拖入音频时间轴可将其插入视频。

MAIN.original: Drag the text box to position it in the video. The time beneath the video title will display the start time of the text.
MAIN.translated: 拖动文本框以改变其在视频中的位置。视频标题下的时间表示文本出现的时间。

MAIN.original: Drag the song to position it in the video. The time beneath the video title will display the start time of the song.
MAIN.translated: 拖动歌曲以改变其在视频中的位置。视频标题下的时间表示歌曲开始播放的时间。

MAIN.original: The Clip Timeline displays all the clips in a video. To jump to a position on the Storyboard, click on the Clip Timeline.
MAIN.translated: 片段时间轴会显示视频中的所有片段。点击片段时间轴可跳跃至Storyboard的某处。

MAIN.original: The Time Scale displays the entire video length and breaks it up into workable segments, making it easy to line up clips, songs and text.
MAIN.translated: 时间轴上会显示视频时长，并将视频分割为可编辑的小段，使排列整理片段、歌曲与文本更加容易。

MAIN.original: To add a transition to the video, drag it between clips on the Storyboard. Transitions can only be viewed in exported videos.
MAIN.translated: 将转场拖入Storyboard上的两个片段之间可添加转场效果。转场效果仅能在导出的视频中查看。

MAIN.original: Click to preview your video. Transitions will not be displayed.
MAIN.translated: 点击预览视频。预览时不会显示转场效果。

MAIN.original: Double-click a clip to open it in the Clip Editor. Clips can be rearranged by copying and pasting or by dragging them into place.
MAIN.translated: 双击片段可将其在片段编辑器中打开。通过复制粘贴与拖动的操作可以重新编排片段。

MAIN.original: The game resolution is too low to export at this quality.
MAIN.translated: 游戏分辨率过低，无法以此质量导出。

MAIN.original: Click to upload the highlighted video to your Online Video Gallery. The uploaded video will be shared on Social Club TV.
MAIN.translated: 点击将选中视频上传至您的在线视频相册。上传的视频将被分享到Social Club TV。

MAIN.original: This window contains all of your uploaded videos. When you upload a video, you will enter your video's tags and description in this window.
MAIN.translated: 此窗口包含了所有您上传的视频。上传视频时，您需要在此窗口中输入视频的标签与描述。

MAIN.original: Social Club failed to initialize. Error code: ~1~. Press Yes to view an online support article to help resolve this issue. Press No to exit.
MAIN.translated: Social Club初始化失败。错误代码：~1~。按「是」查看相关解决方式的支持网页。按「否」退出游戏。~n~~n~注：若为代码1，且游戏版本为1.2.0.32，则需要将系统日期改到20年5月之前或升级游戏。~n~若为代码4，则需要删除根目录下的d3d9.dll以及相关画面Mod。不想删就只能打个破解补丁绕过R星平台。~n~碰碰运气：挂加速器；卸载Rockstar Games Launcher和Rockstar Social Club，重新安装这两个软件。~n~终极解决方法：进入游戏根目录，删除所有文件，验证完整性重装游戏。~n~若以上方法无效或提示其他代码，汉化组也帮不了你哈。

MAIN.translated: 硬盘空间不足，无法导出视频。

MAIN.translated: 已存在同名视频文件。~n~是否要覆盖该文件？

MAIN.original: GTA IV cannot be launched over remote desktop.
MAIN.translated: GTA IV无法在远程桌面下启动。

MAIN.original: Please enter a video title before saving.~n~To enter a title, double click the title entry box above the storyboard.
MAIN.translated: 保存前请输入视频名称。~n~双击Storyboard上方的输入框输入名称。

MAIN.original: Please enter a video title before exporting.~n~To enter a title, double click the title entry box above the storyboard.
MAIN.translated: 导出前请输入视频名称。~n~双击Storyboard上方的输入框输入名称。

Affects video memory, system memory, CPU and GPU performance.

MAIN.original: ~z~Been thinking a lot about war... recently.
MAIN.translated: ~z~Been thinking a lot about war... recently.

MAIN.original: ~z~A lot of it about... a lot of bad stuff in the world.
MAIN.translated: ~z~A lot of it about... a lot of bad stuff in the world.

MAIN.original: ~z~And I was thinking, "What's my favorite war?" Vietnam?
MAIN.translated: ~z~And I was thinking, "What's my favorite war?" Vietnam?

MAIN.original: ~z~What a finale. You know it's over when...
MAIN.translated: ~z~What a finale. You know it's over when...

MAIN.original: ~z~You can't follow that. That's the end.
MAIN.translated: ~z~You can't follow that. That's the end.

MAIN.original: ~z~People are worried about that though, because... the atomic bomb.
MAIN.translated: ~z~People are worried about that though, because... the atomic bomb.

MAIN.original: ~z~It ended a war, which is good.
MAIN.translated: ~z~It ended a war, which is good.

MAIN.original: ~z~But the effects are still being felt, which is bad.
MAIN.translated: ~z~But the effects are still being felt, which is bad.

MAIN.original: ~z~In his, uh... 1907 paper, Einstein said... that light could be described as discreet bundles of energies.
MAIN.translated: ~z~In his, uh... 1907 paper, Einstein said... that light could be described as discreet bundles of energies.

MAIN.original: ~z~That when irradiated, a dof- what sort of cunt thinks like that... really?
MAIN.translated: ~z~That when irradiated, a dof- what sort of cunt thinks like that... really?

MAIN.original: ~z~That's what turned Stephen Hawking mental... too much thinking.
MAIN.translated: ~z~That's what turned Stephen Hawking mental... too much thinking.

MAIN.original: ~z~I'm not a doctor, but I'm pretty sure.
MAIN.translated: ~z~I'm not a doctor, but I'm pretty sure.

MAIN.original: ~z~Yeah, o' course it is, Stephen. Take a day off!
MAIN.translated: ~z~Yeah, o' course it is, Stephen. Take a day off!

MAIN.original: ~z~Go for a walk, or s- not a walk, but....
MAIN.translated: ~z~Go for a walk, or s- not a walk, but....

MAIN.original: ~z~Open a window. Watch a bit o' TV.
MAIN.translated: ~z~Open a window. Watch a bit o' TV.

MAIN.original: ~z~Robot Wars is on. You like that, don't ya?
MAIN.translated: ~z~Robot Wars is on. You like that, don't ya?

MAIN.original: ~z~People go, "Ah well you can't ever cut Steven Hawking. He's a genius."
MAIN.translated: ~z~People go, "Ah well you can't ever cut Steven Hawking. He's a genius."

MAIN.translated: 按~PAD_BACK~切换视角。~n~按~INPUT_PICKUP~退出观看。

Enjoy yourself. Go and see your friend when you're ready to leave.

~r~You missed your date with French Tom.
~s~You have an appointment reminder. This will be displayed 2 hours before a scheduled appointment, and again 30 minutes before.
MAIN.translated: ~s~你有一个约会备忘。它将在约会的两小时前显示，并在约会的半小时前再次显示。

MAIN.original: ~s~The ~BLIP_54~ icon on your radar indicates the location of your date.
MAIN.translated: ~s~小地图上的~BLIP_54~图标表示你的约会地点。

MAIN.translated: 警方留有犯罪者的各种重要信息。

MAIN.original: You can upload photos from a wireless device to find criminals.
MAIN.translated: 你可以通过无线设备上传照片查找犯罪者。

MAIN.original: Select an address to add the criminal to the radar.
MAIN.translated: 选择一个地址以将罪犯位置添加到小地图。

You have ~1~ second to get back in a cop car.

MAIN.translated: 已有支援派出，拒绝增援。

MAIN.original: ~s~You can buy clothes from various clothes shops throughout Liberty City.
MAIN.translated: ~s~你可以在自由城中的各家服装店购买服装。

MAIN.original: ~s~Every item of clothing out on display can be purchased. To buy the clothes, walk up to the item.
MAIN.translated: ~s~货架上的所有服装均可购买。接近商品以购买服装。

MAIN.original: ~s~You will be prompted to press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to try on the clothes.
~s~You can buy the clothes, if you have enough money, by pressing ~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~.
MAIN.translated: ~s~若你有足够的钱，按~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~购买服装。

MAIN.original: ~s~Your first clothes purchase will be free.
MAIN.translated: ~s~你第一次购买的服装是免费的。

MAIN.original: ~s~You can change your clothes back or change into any bought item at a safehouse.
MAIN.translated: ~s~你可以在安全屋中换上你最初的服装，亦可换上任何一件已购买的服装。

MAIN.original: ~s~You cannot buy clothes if there's no one manning the cash register. Control yourself.
MAIN.translated: ~s~若收银台无人负责，你将无法购买服装。管好自己。

MAIN.original: ~s~You cannot buy clothes if there's no one alive to man the cash register. Control yourself.
MAIN.translated: ~s~没有活着的收银员，你将无法购买服装。管好自己。

MAIN.original: If you are arrested by the police you will be processed at a local police precinct.
MAIN.translated: 若被逮捕，你将被移送地方警局。

MAIN.original: The officers will strip you of your weapons and take some of your cash as a bribe.
MAIN.translated: 警察会没收你的武器，并收取一些现金作为贿赂。

MAIN.original: If your health reaches zero, you will pass out and you will be treated at the local medical center.
MAIN.translated: 生命值降为零时，你将会昏迷，然后被送至地方医疗中心进行治疗。

MAIN.original: Before you are discharged, hospital staff will charge you for the healthcare you received.
MAIN.translated: 出院之前，医务人员会向你收取治疗费用。

MAIN.original: ~s~Party mode allows you to play with a group of up to fifteen friends in matches against other parties.
MAIN.translated: ~s~您可以在派对模式中与最多十五个好友一起游玩，并与其他队伍对抗。

MAIN.original: ~s~Paramedics will heal you if you look hurt.~n~They will charge a fee.
MAIN.translated: ~s~若你看上去受伤了，医务人员将会治疗你。这将收取一定费用。

MAIN.original: If the wanted stars are grayed out then the cops have lost sight of you.
MAIN.translated: 通缉星变灰说明警察没有看见你。

MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to leave with your girlfriend.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_PICKUP~跟你的女友一起离开。

MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to cycle through services.~n~Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~ for the $~1~ service.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_PICKUP~切换服务种类。~n~按~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~进行$~1~的服务。

MAIN.original: ~s~When in a suitable vehicle you can pull up next to a prostitute and sound your horn to get them to approach your car.
MAIN.translated: ~s~在合适的载具中时，你可以停到妓女身边，鸣笛让她们上车。

MAIN.original: ~s~Game invites from your friends will be shown here.
MAIN.translated: ~s~来自您好友的游戏邀请将会显示于此。

MAIN.original: ~s~Custom Match allows you to view, filter, and join games of your choosing.
MAIN.translated: ~s~自定对局允许您查看、筛选并加入您选择的游戏。

MAIN.original: ~s~Match Search allows you to view, filter, and join games of your choosing.
MAIN.translated: ~s~对局搜索允许您查看、筛选并加入您选择的游戏。

MAIN.original: ~s~Search for games on a Local Area Network.
~s~Treatment will cost $~1~. ~n~Scare the paramedic off if you don't want it.
MAIN.translated: ~s~治疗将花费$~1~。~n~不想接受治疗则可吓跑医务人员。

MAIN.original: Use ~PAD_DPAD_UP~ or ~PAD_DPAD_DOWN~ to change the channel. Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_LB~ or ~INPUT_FRONTEND_RB~ to change the volume. Press ~PAD_BACK~ to change view. Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to stop watching.
MAIN.translated: 用~PAD_DPAD_UP~~PAD_DPAD_DOWN~换台。按~INPUT_FRONTEND_LB~~INPUT_FRONTEND_RB~调节音量。按~PAD_BACK~切换视角。按~INPUT_PICKUP~停止观看。

MAIN.original: Press ~PAD_DPAD_UP~ or ~PAD_DPAD_DOWN~ to change the channel. Use ~INPUT_FRONTEND_LT~ or ~INPUT_FRONTEND_RT~ to change the volume. Press ~PAD_BACK~ to change view. Press ~INPUT_PICKUP~ to stop watching.
MAIN.translated: 按~PAD_DPAD_UP~~PAD_DPAD_DOWN~换台。用~INPUT_FRONTEND_LT~~INPUT_FRONTEND_RT~调节音量。按~PAD_BACK~切换视角。按~INPUT_PICKUP~停止观看。

MAIN.original: ~s~When in this view the camera can be moved using ~PAD_RSTICK_ALL~.
MAIN.translated: ~s~这一视角下，可通过~PAD_RSTICK_ALL~移动镜头。

MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_ENTER~ to enter the cable car.
You are on the cable car to Colony Island. ~n~Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~ to skip there.
MAIN.translated: 你乘坐的是前往Colony岛的缆车。~n~按~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~跳过动画。

MAIN.original: You are on the cable car to Algonquin. ~n~Press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~ to skip there.
MAIN.translated: 你乘坐的是前往Algonquin的缆车。~n~按~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~跳过动画。

MAIN.original: The police have stopped the cable cars.
~s~You must lose your wanted level before starting the multiplayer tutorial.
MAIN.translated: ~s~开始多人游戏教程前，你必须摆脱通缉。

MAIN.original: Head over to ~e~ and take out the ~r~criminal.
In order to corner effectively press ~INPUT_VEH_BRAKE~ to use the brake.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_VEH_BRAKE~使用刹车以更好地转弯。

MAIN.original: To maintain control of your vehicle use ~INPUT_VEH_BRAKE~ to apply the brakes.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_VEH_BRAKE~使用刹车以更好地控制载具。

MAIN.original: Select the SIXAXIS™ tutorial from the phone menu to playthrough a tutorial that will show how to use SIXAXIS™.
MAIN.translated: 在手机菜单中选择SIXAXIS™教程以游玩关于SIXAXIS™用法的教程。

MAIN.original: If movement is proving difficult, it might be best to get a cab to take you where you are going.
MAIN.translated: 若难以行动，说不定还是打的去目的地比较好。

MAIN.original: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!
MAIN.translated: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!

MAIN.original: ~s~You can add your own icon via the pause menu map screen that will add a route on the radar.
MAIN.translated: ~s~你可以在暂停菜单的地图界面中向小地图添加一个导航点。

MAIN.original: You can now do activities with Roman as well as working with him, he will phone you or you can phone him and arrange them.
MAIN.translated: 你现在可以与Roman进行各种活动，也能替他干活。他会打电话找你，你也可以主动打给他进行安排。

MAIN.original: You can now go on activities with Roman as well as working with him, phone him back to arrange an alternative activity, or he may phone you.
MAIN.translated: 你现在可以与Roman进行各种活动，~n~也能替他干活。他会打电话找你，你也能打给他安排活动。

MAIN.original: Enter the marker to trigger the mission.
Press ~INPUT_VEH_EXIT~ to dive out of a moving car.
You can save any vehicle in the parking spot outside your safehouse. Park your car there and exit it. The car will remain there for you to use.
MAIN.translated: 你可以在安全屋外的停车位存放任何载具。将车停入车位后下车，即可保存车辆留待日后使用。

MAIN.original: To replenish your health you can visit fast food vendors, like hotdog stands, around the city.
MAIN.translated: 你可以拜访城市中的各种小吃摊恢复生命值，比如热狗摊。

MAIN.original: Hold ~INPUT_SPRINT~ to run. Tap ~INPUT_SPRINT~ repeatedly to sprint.
Press ~INPUT_ENTER~ to enter or exit a vehicle.
The number of stars on screen shows your wanted level. With a wanted level cops will attempt to bust you.
MAIN.translated: 画面上的星星数量表示你的通缉度。具有通缉度时警察会尝试逮捕你。

MAIN.original: The area cops search is shown by the flashing red and blue zone. Cops are shown by the flashing red and blue icons.
MAIN.translated: 小地图上闪烁的区域表示警方的搜捕范围。范围内的警察会用红蓝交替闪烁的圆点标识。

MAIN.original: To lose your wanted level, escape the flashing zone.
MAIN.translated: 逃出闪烁区域以降低通缉度。

MAIN.original: Hold ~INPUT_VEH_HEADLIGHT~ to switch headlights between full beam and dimmed.
Press ~INPUT_VEH_HEADLIGHT~ to switch headlights between full beam and dimmed.
You can now call Roman for work. Find Roman in the phonebook and select the Job option.
MAIN.translated: 现在你可以打给Roman接活。在通讯录中找到Roman后选择「差事」。

MAIN.original: You can now do some extra work for Jacob. Call Jacob using the Job option on your phone.
MAIN.translated: 你现在可以替Jacob做些私活。使用手机中的差事选项呼叫Jacob。

MAIN.original: To dial a number with your phone you will need to access the phone. Press ~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~ to activate the phone.
MAIN.translated: 用手机拨号前需要先拿出手机。~n~按~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~拿出手机。

MAIN.original: Stop near Roman, or press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ to sound your horn to attract his attention.
MAIN.translated: 停到Roman附近，或按~INPUT_VEH_HORN~鸣笛引起他的注意。

MAIN.original: Stop near Roman, or press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ to sound your horn to attract his attention.
MAIN.translated: 停到Roman附近，或按~INPUT_VEH_HORN~鸣笛引起他的注意。

MAIN.original: Stop near Roman and he'll get in the car.
Make your choice: Rescue Roman or go on a date with Michelle...
MAIN.translated: 抉择：去救 Roman 还是与 Michelle 约会...

MAIN.original: You can call Roman to inform him of the situation.
MAIN.translated: 你可以打给Roman向他说明情况。

MAIN.original: You can watch TV in your apartment.
MAIN.translated: 你可以在你的公寓中看电视。

MAIN.original: ~s~Press ~INPUT_VEH_HANDBRAKE~ to use the handbrake. ~n~Press ~PAD_A~ for alternative handbrake (Standard controls).
MAIN.translated: ~s~按~INPUT_VEH_HANDBRAKE~使用手刹。~n~按~PAD_A~也是手刹(标准键位下)。

MAIN.original: You can make changes to your phone profile at any point. You can customize ringtype and ringtone.
MAIN.translated: 你可以随时更改手机的设置，还可以自定义铃声和响铃模式。

MAIN.original: If you get a better phone you'll have more customizable options, such as different themes.
MAIN.translated: 若你拥有更好的手机，可自定义的内容也会变多，例如更换主题。

MAIN.original: GTA IV allows you to capture recent events for playback at a later time. You can capture the most recent events by holding ~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~.
MAIN.translated: GTA IV 允许您在事件发生后捕捉最近事件用于回放。长按~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~可以捕捉最近事件。

MAIN.original: GTA IV allows you to capture recent events for playback at a later time. You can capture the most recent events by pressing ~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~.
MAIN.translated: GTA IV 允许您在事件发生后捕捉最近事件用于回放。长按~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~可以捕捉最近事件。

MAIN.original: You can capture clips of recent events by holding ~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~. These clips can be edited within the Video Editor accessed through the cellphone.
MAIN.translated: 长按~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~可以捕捉最近事件的片段。这些片段可以通过手机中的「视频编辑器」编辑。

MAIN.original: You can capture clips of recent events by pressing ~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~. These clips can be edited within the Video Editor accessed through the cellphone.
MAIN.translated: 长按~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~可以捕捉最近事件的片段。这些片段可以通过手机中的「视频编辑器」编辑。

MAIN.original: Select this option to access the Video Editor. Hold ~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~ to capture clips.
MAIN.translated: 选择此项启动视频编辑器。~n~长按~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~捕捉片段。

MAIN.original: Select this option to access the Video Editor. Press ~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~ to capture clips.
MAIN.translated: 选择此项启动视频编辑器。~n~长按~INPUT_REPLAY_SAVE_TO_HDD~捕捉片段。

MAIN.original: Your Clip has been captured. If you wish to view or edit your clip, bring up your phone and select Video Editor.
MAIN.translated: 片段已捕捉。若想查看或编辑片段，拿出手机后选择「视频编辑器」。

MAIN.original: ~s~Hold ~INPUT_VEH_CIN_CAM~ to focus the camera on the target vehicle.
MAIN.translated: ~s~按住~INPUT_VEH_CIN_CAM~可将镜头对准目标车辆。

MAIN.original: ~s~Go to the internet cafe and check your emails.
You cannot reply to Brucie's email while on a mission.
MAIN.translated: 你不能在任务期间回复Brucie的邮件。

MAIN.original: You cannot reply to Brucie's email while saving.
MAIN.translated: 你不能在存档时回复Brucie的邮件。

MAIN.original: You cannot reply to Brucie's email right now.
MAIN.translated: 你现在不能回复Brucie的邮件。

MAIN.original: You must reply to Brucie's email if you intend to steal the car for him.
MAIN.translated: 若你想替Brucie偷车，就必须回复他的邮件。

MAIN.original: You must reply to Brucie's email if you intend to steal the bike for him.
MAIN.translated: 若你想替Brucie偷车，就必须回复他的邮件。

MAIN.original: To hotwire a vehicle faster repeatedly press ~INPUT_VEH_HOTWIRE_LEFT~ or ~INPUT_VEH_HOTWIRE_RIGHT~.
Dimitri is not here. Return between 5pm and 3am.
MAIN.translated: Dimitri现在不在。请在下午五点到凌晨三点间找他。

MAIN.original: Little Jacob is now your friend, he will phone you or you can phone him to arrange activities.
MAIN.translated: Little Jacob现在是你的朋友了，他会打电话找你，你也可以主动打给他进行安排。

MAIN.original: Little Jacob is now your friend, you can phone him back to arrange an alternative activity, or he may phone you.
MAIN.translated: Little Jacob现在是你的朋友了，他会打电话找你，你也能打给他安排活动。

MAIN.original: Stop near Little Jacob, or press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ to sound your horn to attract Little Jacob's attention.
MAIN.translated: 停到Little Jacob附近，或按~INPUT_VEH_HORN~鸣笛引起他的注意。

MAIN.original: Stop near Little Jacob, or press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ to sound your horn to attract Little Jacob's attention.
MAIN.translated: 停到Little Jacob附近，或按~INPUT_VEH_HORN~鸣笛引起他的注意。

MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ to sound your horn to attract Little Jacob's attention.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_VEH_HORN~鸣笛引起Little Jacob的注意。

MAIN.original: Stop near Little Jacob and he'll get in the car.
MAIN.translated: 停到Little Jacob附近他就会上车。

MAIN.original: The cops are less likely to identify you if you swap vehicles or run through alleyways and side streets.
MAIN.translated: 若你更换载具或在小巷中穿行，警察发现你的几率就会降低。

MAIN.original: To access the keypad press ~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~ from the initial cellphone screen.
MAIN.translated: 在手机主界面按下~INPUT_PHONE_TAKE_OUT~以使用数字键盘。

MAIN.original: The circle around the radar represents your health and body armor. The green left half of the circle is your health. As you lose health the green will fade out. The right half of the circle is your body armor.
MAIN.translated: 环绕小地图的圆圈表示你的生命值与护甲值。左半圈的绿色表示你的生命值，你的生命值降低时绿色会减少。右半圈表示你的护甲值。

MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ to sound your horn to attract Roman's attention.
Press ~INPUT_NEXT_CAMERA~ to select different camera modes. Hold ~INPUT_VEH_CIN_CAM~ while in a car to select cinematic camera mode.
MAIN.translated: 按~INPUT_NEXT_CAMERA~切换不同的视角。在车内时按住~INPUT_VEH_CIN_CAM~可启用电影式视角。

MAIN.original: When in cinematic mode if you press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ you will switch on slow motion mode. Press ~INPUT_VEH_HORN~ again to return to normal speed.
MAIN.translated: 在电影式视角模式下，按~INPUT_VEH_HORN~切换慢动作模式。再次按~INPUT_VEH_HORN~可恢复正常速度。

MAIN.original: Occasionally, calling a contact to find out what they're doing will open up scenarios earlier than if you waited to be called. You can try calling Roman.
MAIN.translated: 有时，打电话询问联系人他的情况可以比等待他的电话更早触发剧情。你可以试试打给Roman。

MAIN.original: You can place a Waypoint on the map and a GPS route will be displayed to that location.
MAIN.translated: 你可以在地图上选定一个导航点，然后地图上就会显示导航路线。

MAIN.original: Press ~PAD_START~ to go to the pause menu. When on the map screen press ~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~ to place your Waypoint. This will give you a GPS route to the location you have marked on the map.
MAIN.translated: 按~PAD_START~进入暂停菜单。处在地图界面时，按~INPUT_FRONTEND_ACCEPT~选定导航点，然后地图上就会显示对应的导航路线。

MAIN.original: Press ~INPUT_SPRINT~ to break out when being disarmed by the police.
MAIN.translated: 被警察控制住时，按~INPUT_SPRINT~抗捕。

MAIN.original: Use ~INPUT_SPRINT~ to break out when being disarmed by the police.

MAIN.original: Roman now likes you a lot - you can use his special ability. You can call up Roman and select "Car Service" he will send you one of his cabs to pick you up and take you to destinations around the city.

MAIN.translated: Jacob现在很喜欢你，你可以使用他的特殊能力了。呼叫Jacob时选择「枪支」，他就会到你附近的某地向你以低价出售武器装备。

MAIN.original: ~m~Kill the other players as many times as you can. The player with the most cash when the game ends wins. Remember to graciously loot the cash dropped by dead players.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Kill the other players as many times as you can. The player with the most cash when the game ends wins. Remember to graciously loot the cash dropped by dead players.

MAIN.original: ~m~Take the other crew down. The crew with the most cash at the end wins. Remember to loot the cash dropped by deceased players. That's the way to get ahead.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Take the other crew down. The crew with the most cash at the end wins. Remember to loot the cash dropped by deceased players. That's the way to get ahead.

MAIN.original: ~m~Doing the Mafiya's orders is a cut-throat business. Complete contracts before the competition does and get the rewards. The player with the most cash at the end wins.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Doing the Mafiya's orders is a cut-throat business. Complete contracts before the competition does and get the rewards. The player with the most cash at the end wins.

MAIN.original: ~m~You're a member of a crew doing contract work for the Mafiya. Complete contracts before the competition does and get the rewards. The crew with most cash at the end wins.
MAIN.translated: ~m~You're a member of a crew doing contract work for the Mafiya. Complete contracts before the competition does and get the rewards. The crew with most cash at the end wins.

MAIN.original: ~m~Your crew has to get hold of whatever cars the boss wants. Pay will depend on the condition of the car, unless it's stuffed with ~g~drugs.~m~ Whichever crew makes the most money wins. Simple. ~b~Vehicles~m~ are represented by blue markers on the radar and the ~y~drop off points~m~ as yellow markers.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Your crew has to get hold of whatever cars the boss wants. Pay will depend on the condition of the car, unless it's stuffed with ~g~drugs.~m~ Whichever crew makes the most money wins. Simple. ~b~Vehicles~m~ are represented by blue markers on the radar and the ~y~drop off points~m~ as yellow markers.

MAIN.original: ~m~Steal whatever car the boss wants. Pay will depend on the condition of the car, unless it's stuffed with ~g~drugs.~m~ Whoever makes the most money wins. It's America, for beginners. ~b~Vehicles~m~ are represented by blue markers on the radar and the ~y~drop off points~m~ as yellow markers.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Steal whatever car the boss wants. Pay will depend on the condition of the car, unless it's stuffed with ~g~drugs.~m~ Whoever makes the most money wins. It's America, for beginners. ~b~Vehicles~m~ are represented by blue markers on the radar and the ~y~drop off points~m~ as yellow markers.

MAIN.original: ~m~Race to the finish, passing through each checkpoint in order. Hold ~INPUT_VEH_EXIT~ to respawn your vehicle on the last checkpoint passed.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Race to the finish, passing through each checkpoint in order. Hold ~INPUT_VEH_EXIT~ to respawn your vehicle on the last checkpoint passed.

MAIN.original: ~m~Starting on foot, get from the starting position to the finish line by any means necessary. First one there wins.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Starting on foot, get from the starting position to the finish line by any means necessary. First one there wins.

MAIN.original: ~m~Starting on foot, get to the next point on the map however you can. Proceed through the points in order. First one to finish wins.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Starting on foot, get to the next point on the map however you can. Proceed through the points in order. First one to finish wins.

MAIN.original: ~m~Race and fight your way through the checkpoints in order and then hit the finish. You can only hold one drive-by weapon at a time, hold ~INPUT_VEH_HEADLIGHT~ to drop your currently selected weapon when in a vehicle.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Race and fight your way through the checkpoints in order and then hit the finish. You can only hold one drive-by weapon at a time, hold ~INPUT_VEH_HEADLIGHT~ to drop your currently selected weapon when in a vehicle.

MAIN.original: ~m~Race and fight your way through the checkpoints in order and then hit the finish. You can only hold one drive-by weapon at a time, use ~INPUT_DROP_WEAPON~ to drop your currently selected weapon when in a vehicle.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Race and fight your way through the checkpoints in order and then hit the finish. You can only hold one drive-by weapon at a time, use ~INPUT_DROP_WEAPON~ to drop your currently selected weapon when in a vehicle.

MAIN.original: ~m~Starting on foot, get from the starting position to the finish line by any means necessary. First one there wins.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Starting on foot, get from the starting position to the finish line by any means necessary. First one there wins.

MAIN.original: ~m~Starting on foot, get to the next point on the map however you can. Proceed through the points in order. First one to finish wins.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Starting on foot, get to the next point on the map however you can. Proceed through the points in order. First one to finish wins.

MAIN.original: ~m~Each gang has to take out the opposing team and steal more drugs.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Each gang has to take out the opposing team and steal more drugs.

MAIN.original: ~m~The ~COL_NET_1~crooks~m~ must get their ~COL_NET_1~Boss~m~ to safety.~n~The ~COL_NET_2~cops~m~ have got to take down the boss. The boss is marked with a crosshair.
MAIN.translated: ~m~The ~COL_NET_1~crooks~m~ must get their ~COL_NET_1~Boss~m~ to safety.~n~The ~COL_NET_2~cops~m~ have got to take down the boss. The boss is marked with a crosshair.

MAIN.original: ~m~Turf generates cash for a crew while they have control of it. So get control of it. Take some turf by occupying it for a period. The more members of your crew on that patch of turf, the quicker you will gain control. If the rival gang is near a patch of turf, you can't take control.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Turf generates cash for a crew while they have control of it. So get control of it. Take some turf by occupying it for a period. The more members of your crew on that patch of turf, the quicker you will gain control. If the rival gang is near a patch of turf, you can't take control.

MAIN.original: ~m~A major deal is going down. Head over there with your crew and rip both parties off. Get hold of the merchandise and get out of there. No one can know that Kenny Petrovic was behind this, so get rid of all witnesses.
MAIN.translated: ~m~A major deal is going down. Head over there with your crew and rip both parties off. Get hold of the merchandise and get out of there. No one can know that Kenny Petrovic was behind this, so get rid of all witnesses.

MAIN.original: ~m~The authorities have surrounded Francis International to take down Kenny Petrovic. Escape with him and the rest of your crew before the NOOSE tightens. You'll need to get some transport first.
MAIN.translated: ~m~The authorities have surrounded Francis International to take down Kenny Petrovic. Escape with him and the rest of your crew before the NOOSE tightens. You'll need to get some transport first.

MAIN.original: ~m~A rival export business has a ship sitting in the docks waiting to be loaded. You must steal the explosives, gain access to the ship and plant two bombs, one on the bridge, the other in the hold. Make sure you're not on the ship when she blows. Those are Mr. Petrovic's orders.
MAIN.translated: ~m~A rival export business has a ship sitting in the docks waiting to be loaded. You must steal the explosives, gain access to the ship and plant two bombs, one on the bridge, the other in the hold. Make sure you're not on the ship when she blows. Those are Mr. Petrovic's orders.

MAIN.original: ~m~Kick back. Liberty City is your playground, only your playmates ain't so nice. Have fun out there.
MAIN.translated: ~m~Kick back. Liberty City is your playground, only your playmates ain't so nice. Have fun out there.

MAIN.original: The ~COL_NET_1~crooks~m~ need to look out for each other while they escape. The ~COL_NET_2~cops~m~ have got to take the crew down. There are no second chances, so make your first one count.
MAIN.translated: The ~COL_NET_1~crooks~m~ need to look out for each other while they escape. The ~COL_NET_2~cops~m~ have got to take the crew down. There are no second chances, so make your first one count.

MAIN.original: Whew! It is hotter than holy hell out there! Time for BBQs, ice cold beers and a spike in crime rates.
MAIN.translated: 呼！今天外面真的是热死人啦！很适合烧烤配冰啤酒，也适合犯罪率暴涨。

MAIN.original: Sunshine today in Liberty City, puts everyone in a good mood, hard working Americans and single mother immigrants alike. Enjoy!
MAIN.translated: 今天自由城天气晴朗，让人心情舒畅，努力工作的美国公民和单亲移民妈妈也不例外。

MAIN.original: It's sunny out there, but blowing a fierce wind, be aware folks, you can almost smell Alderney.
MAIN.translated: 今天天气晴朗，但有强风。注意了各位，甚至能闻到 Alderney 的臭味。

MAIN.original: Overcast today, a storm may be blowing, are you prepared? It might be time to get scared and irrational, keep watching Weazel for updates.
MAIN.translated: 今天是个阴天，暴风雨或将来临，你准备好了吗？是时候抛弃理性开始害怕了。关注Weazel获取最新消息。

MAIN.original: It's raining out there folks, let's hope it washes away some of the liberal garbage and amoral sludge that runs through Liberty City's streets.
MAIN.translated: 现在正在下雨，各位。希望这场雨能冲走自由城街头巷尾的自由派废物和没良心人渣。

MAIN.original: Nothing but a pathetic drizzle out there today, nothing to worry about. When it's time to worry, Weazel will let you know first.
MAIN.translated: 今天只是一场小雨，无需担心。该担心的时候，Weazel会立刻通知你的。

MAIN.original: Who says be kind to the environment? It's no friend to us. The fog out there is denser than a jury on a celebrity murder trial, yep, you'll need a powerful, American SUV to cut through this.
MAIN.translated: 有必要对自然环境友好吗？它又不是我们的朋友。外面的雾现在比名人谋杀案的陪审团的脸皮都厚。没错，只有动力强劲的国产SUV才能助你前进。

MAIN.original: There are bolts from the heavens showering down on Liberty City, to some, static electricity; to others, a display of His anger at the sins of mankind - you decide.
MAIN.translated: 自由城上空天雷滚滚。有人认为是静电现象，有人认为是人类罪行引起神怒——自己选吧。

MAIN.original: You can search for Singles in your area. Just select your fancy below.
MAIN.translated: 您可以查找您所在地区的单身人士。请在下方选择你喜欢的对象。

MAIN.original: This website for child beauty pageants has been shut down.
MAIN.translated: 此儿童选美网站已被封停

MAIN.original: Your IP address has been cataloged and an investigator will be contacting you soon.
MAIN.translated: 您的IP地址已被记录，日后将会有调查人员来联系您

MAIN.original: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!
MAIN.translated: THIS LABEL NEEDS TO BE HERE !!!

MAIN.original: Niko, I have some more cab work - call me for a job. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，我这儿还有拉客的活，接单找我。Rom

MAIN.original: I needed a lift home from hospital but you didn't pick up. Please tell me you had your face buried in some nice titties at least. Rom
MAIN.translated: 我需要你来医院接我的时候你没来。你至少得享受到洗面奶才对得起我吧。Rom

MAIN.original: Cuz, thanks for doing this work for Vlad. He's an asshole but I owe him money. What you going to do? Rom
MAIN.translated: 堂弟，谢谢你替Vlad把这事办了。他就是个混蛋，不过谁让我欠他钱呢。接下来你怎么做？Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, remember if you want some money you can call me for a cab job. Rom.
MAIN.translated: Niko，记住，你想赚钱的话可以找我接单开出租。Rom

MAIN.original: Shit, Niko. They're going to find out we killed Vlad. I know it. Our bodies are gonna be in the Humboldt next to Vlad's... Shit. Rom
MAIN.translated: 完了，Niko。他们会发现是我们杀了Vlad的。我明白的。我们的尸体会和Vlad的一块儿沉到Humboldt河河底的。Rom

MAIN.original: Hey Cuz, thanks for saving my ass back there. I thought I'd played my last hand when that biker guy kidnapped me for the Russians. You're a fucking hero, man. Rom
MAIN.translated: 嘿，堂弟，感谢你能来救我。那个飞车党替俄国佬绑架我的时候，我都以为自己要没命了。你丫就是大英雄，老弟。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, you came to Liberty for penthouses, women, fast cars. Don't throw it away for revenge. Darko did not help, remember? Do the deal and maybe we can take a private jet down to Vice City!!
MAIN.translated: Niko，你来自由城就是为了公寓女人跟跑车。别为了复仇抛弃这些。Darko那次就没啥用，记得么？去交易吧，说不定我们还能开私人飞机去罪城！！

MAIN.original: Niko - come see me at the depot. There is someone I want you to meet. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，来车行找我。我想给你介绍个人。Rom

MAIN.original: Why did you leave me behind, Cuz? That's not cool. You cut out on me like I was a one night stand. Rom
MAIN.translated: 你为什么要抛下我，堂弟？那可不行。搞得跟我和你搞一夜情一样，挥之即去。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, imagine the honeymoon I can take Mallorie on if you do this deal. Come on, do it for me - I am your cousin. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，想象一下你去交易的话我就能带Mallorie去度蜜月吧。拜托，为了我你也去交易吧。我是你堂兄啊。Rom

MAIN.original: Shit. Need help. Come to the depot quick, man! Rom
MAIN.translated: 靠。求救。速来车行，老弟！ Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, I'm at the church. I'm getting married. Wear some smart clothes and get over here as soon as you can. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，我现在在教堂。我要结婚了。穿套像样的衣服赶紧过来。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, I'm getting married tomorrow. Get lots of sleep - I need you to be at the church for 10am. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，明天我就要结婚了。今晚好好睡，明早十点你一定要到教堂。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, I'm getting married at 10 tomorrow morning. My last night as a single man. Go home, get some sleep and meet me at the church. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，明早十点我就要结婚了。今晚是我一个人睡的最后一夜了。回家吧，好好睡一觉，明早教堂见。Rom

MAIN.original: My wedding day is here, cuz! Be at the church at 10 o'clock. And wear some smart clothes, I don't want you looking scruffy. Rom
MAIN.translated: 今天我要结婚啦，堂弟！十点到教堂。鞋子穿好点，我不想你看上去乱糟糟的。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, Remember to check your email. Brucie might have some work for you. We can start rolling with the bling like he does?! Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，记得检查你的邮箱。Brucie可能有活给你。我们也可以像他那样穿金戴银吗？！Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, I'm on my way to hospital in an ambulance. You ignored my call and they beat me up. They say they're going to get me again.
MAIN.translated: Niko，我现在在救护车上往医院去。你无视了我的电话，他们把我打了一顿，还说以后还来找我。

MAIN.original: Niko, you need to get over here. I think your balls must be getting very jealous of mine. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，你得来这儿玩玩。我想你的把柄肯定会嫉妒我的把柄的。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, have you heard from your boyfriend yet? Check your email at the TW@ internet cafe. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，有收到你小男朋友的消息吗？去TW@网咖看看你的邮箱。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, come see me man. Rom
Niko, I'm at the gentlemen's club! Check this ass out. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，我现在在绅士俱乐部！瞧这屁股。Rom

MAIN.original: Stay in touch, Cousin. I feel as though we are drifting apart. Rom
MAIN.translated: 保持联络，堂弟。我都感觉我们渐行渐远了。Rom

MAIN.original: Why don't I ever see you, Niko. You spending too much time chasing titties and avoiding your cousin. Let's hang out. Rom
MAIN.translated: 我怎么从没见过你，Niko。你花在咪咪的时间上太多了，一直躲着你堂兄。我们去走走吧。Rom

MAIN.original: Too bad you can't be hanging with me, cuz. Let's do something soon. Rom
MAIN.translated: 你不能跟我出门真是太糟了，堂弟。我们出去转转吧。Rom

MAIN.original: Okay, Niko. Are you dead? I don't want to have to call your mother. Let's hang out if you're still breathing. Rom
MAIN.translated: 好吧，Niko，你是死了吗？我可不想给你妈打电话。你要是还活着，我们就出去转转吧。Rom

MAIN.original: You should have called to cancel, cuz. You probably met a hot woman, yes? Call me soon. Rom
MAIN.translated: 你应该打个电话跟我说的，堂弟。你是不是遇到辣妹了？尽快打给我。Rom

MAIN.original: Thanks for standing me up, Cuz. I met a smoking hot air stewardess while waiting. She felt sorry for me and gave me some first class service. Rom
MAIN.translated: 谢谢你鸽了我啊，堂弟。等你的时候我遇到了一个性感到爆的空姐。她见我可怜就给我来了点头等舱服务。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko, what's going on? Why'd you stand me up? Drug dealing and killing more important than spending time with family? Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko，怎么回事？你咋把我鸽了？贩毒跟杀人比和家人在一起还重要吗？Rom

MAIN.original: Yo, NB. You left me hanging. Call me next time you can't make it to an appointment. It'll give me time to arrange a date with a hot bored housewife. Rom
MAIN.translated: 哟，NB。你把我晾一边了。下次你来不了就给我打个电话。这样我还能来得及去约个性感的寂寞人妻。Rom

MAIN.original: Niko! Anytime you need a ride to anywhere give me a call, I'll send one of my drivers to pick you up. Rom
MAIN.translated: Niko！你要是需要乘车去哪儿，随时给我打电话，我会派手下的司机来接你的。Rom

MAIN.original: NB. Yellow cabs are too expensive, I don't want you wasting your money. Call me if you want me to send a driver. Rom
MAIN.translated: NB。黄出租太贵了，我不想你浪费自己的钱。要我派车的话就给我打电话。Rom

MAIN.original: What's the point in owning a car service if you can't give family free rides, call me if you want me to send a driver. Rom
MAIN.translated: 要是自己的家人都不能免费乘车的话，做叫车服务的生意还有什么意义。需要我派车的时候就打个电话。Rom

MAIN.original: I'm getting tired of sending all my cars to the airport to pick up 80 year old Vice City residents. Call if you want me to send you one. Rom
MAIN.translated: 我不想再把车全派到机场去接八十高龄的罪城老头老太了。你要车就给我打电话。Rom

MAIN.original: I made it home from the hospital by myself. A lot of good you are, cousin. Rom
MAIN.translated: 我成功自己从医院回家了。你真是给好人，堂弟。Rom

MAIN.original: I had to get one of the nurses to take me home. I'd be pissed off with you if she hadn't given me a sponge bath with a happy ending. Rom
MAIN.translated: 我只能找护士送我回家。要不是她给我她替我擦了身子，帮我撸了一发，我早就对你大发雷霆了。Rom

MAIN.original: Thought you would want to know I got home by myself, Cuz. I'm not lying dead in the street. Rom
MAIN.translated: 你应该想知道我自己回家了吧，堂弟。我没有暴毙街头。Rom

MAIN.original: NB, ended up taking the bus back from hospital. Met this Danish backpacker who just arrived in the city. I took her back to her hotel and showed her a side of Liberty she's not going to forget. Rom
MAIN.translated: NB，我最后乘公交从医院回来了。遇到了一个刚到这儿的丹麦游客。我送她回了她的宾馆，给她留下了对自由州难以磨灭的印象。Rom

MAIN.original: Had to get one of the drivers to get me back from hospital. Man, that guy don't like doing favours. Try and pick me up next time. Rom
MAIN.translated: 最后只能让手下的司机来医院接我。老弟，那家伙不喜欢送人情。下次尽量来接我吧。Rom

MAIN.original: Why didn't you come to the hospital? Hope you're okay. Rom
MAIN.translated: 你怎么没来医院？希望你没事。Rom

MAIN.original: Got one of the drivers to pick me up from hospital when you didn't show. I think he might get more action than me and Brucie combined. Man is a legend. Rom
MAIN.translated: 你没来，我就只能让手下的司机来医院接我了。我觉得他下过的手比我跟Brucie加起来还多。这哥们就是个传奇。Rom

MAIN.original: NB, you must be real busy with killing at the moment if you can't pick me up from hospital. I'm surprised the ER wasn't full of your victims. Rom
MAIN.translated: NB，既然你没空来接我，那一定是忙着杀人吧。Rom

MAIN.original: NB - you been on your gay date yet? I know you want to do it! Don't be nervous and check your emails. - Rom
MAIN.translated: NB，你有没有去见过你的基佬男友啊？我知道你很想去的！别紧张，记得看看邮箱。 - Rom

MAIN.original: Hey man, try not to fall in love with that guy when you go on a date with him. This is business not pleasure. He's probably emailed you by now. - Rom
MAIN.translated: 嘿，老弟，跟那老兄约会的时候可别假戏真做了。你是去干活的，不是找乐子的。估计他已经给你发邮件了。 - Rom

MAIN.original: Hey cuz, maybe it's all that juice, but Brucie is getting really anxious about you going on that date with French Tom or whatever. You checked your emails? - Rom
MAIN.translated: 嘿，堂弟，可能是那药的关系，Brucie现在对你和那个French Tom约会的事情好像很紧张。你有看过你的邮箱吗？ - Rom

MAIN.original: Shit, where are you? I'm not having this wedding without my cousin the Church is closing soon. Get here! - Rom
MAIN.translated: 我靠，你人呢？我不会在堂弟你不在的情况下开始婚礼的，再这样教堂都要关门了。快来！ - Rom

MAIN.original: Cuz, if any hot girls call you on this phone looking for a threesome with the one and only Roman Bellic then give them my new number! - Rom
MAIN.translated: 堂弟，要是有哪个性感辣妹打给你这个号码找别无分号的Roman Bellic玩3P，就给她们我的新号！ - Rom

MAIN.original: Cuz, you left me in the club. You go home to bang one of the girls? Have fun, you animal. - Rom
MAIN.translated: 堂弟，你把我扔在俱乐部了。你是带了一个妞回去睡吗？祝你玩得开心，禽兽。 - Rom

MAIN.original: Cuz, where'd you go? Got left in the club by myself. More titties for me, I guess. Later. - Rom
MAIN.translated: 堂弟，你去哪了？我被一个人落在俱乐部里了。也许我能找到更多奶子。回见。 - Rom

MAIN.original: Cousin, my other drivers got jealous about you taking all the fares. I've nearly got a mutiny on my hands. You're going to have to earn your money with your fists and not my cabs from now on. Let's hang out. - Rom
MAIN.translated: 堂弟，我手下的几个司机因为你把所有单子都抢了这事眼睛都绿了。他们差点就要造反了。从现在起，你得靠自己的拳头而不是我的的士挣钱了。有空我们去走走吧。 - Rom

MAIN.original: Yokel, come see me for more work. - Vlad
MAIN.translated: 乡巴佬，来给我干活。- Vlad

MAIN.original: Niko, you missed our date. What happened? I hope you haven't got caught up in something. Call me. xx
MAIN.translated: Niko，你没来我们的约会。怎么回事？希望你不是遇上什么麻烦了。联系我。xx

MAIN.original: Niko, you didn't show up for our date. Are you involved with some criminals or something like that. I hope you're okay. xx
MAIN.translated: Niko，我怎么没见着你赴约。你是和什么罪犯之类的扯上关系了吗。希望你没事。xx

MAIN.original: Umm. I waited for you and you didn't show. Did something else come up. I'd love to know what you do with your time. xx
MAIN.translated: 唔，我一直在等你，然后你没来。是突然有别的事吗。我很想知道你那会儿在干什么。xx

MAIN.original: Well, Niko. I waited for you thinking we had a date. What exactly were you doing instead?
MAIN.translated: 好吧，Niko。我记得我们要约会，就等了你很久。不来约会你到底干嘛去了？

MAIN.original: If you're not going to show up to our dates, at least tell me what you do with your time. Are you involved with some bad people?
MAIN.translated: 要是你不能赴约，至少也告诉我你去干嘛了吧。你该不会和某些坏人在一起吧？

MAIN.original: I guess I should expect to be stood up and stuff like that when I'm dating a criminal. That's what you are, isn't it?
MAIN.translated: 我早该知道跟罪犯约会的时候会被放鸽子。你就是罪犯，对吧？

MAIN.original: Sorry, I'm busy. Speak soon. xx
Your attention is really flattering but I've got my hands full at the mo. Speak soon. xx
MAIN.translated: 你对我的关注很讨喜，不过现在我很忙。有空再聊。xx

MAIN.original: Sorry, I'm on another assignment. Talk to you in a while. xx
MAIN.translated: 抱歉，现在有工作要忙。之后再跟你聊。xx

MAIN.original: Niko, can you please stop calling me. I'm unavailable for a while. We'll talk soon though. xx
MAIN.translated: Niko，能不能拜托你别打给我了。我现在没空。要聊之后可以聊。 xx

MAIN.original: I can't talk to you at the moment. Please stop calling for the time being. xx
MAIN.translated: 我现在没法跟你讲电话。麻烦先别打给我了。xx

MAIN.original: Niko, you're going to have to stop calling for a bit. I need some me time. xx
MAIN.translated: Niko，求你先别给我打电话了。我需要一些私人时间。xx

MAIN.original: Niko, where did you go? I couldn't find you. Did something important come up? Are you involved with some bad people?
MAIN.translated: Niko，你去哪了？我没见着你。是突然有什么急事吗？你该不会和某些坏人在一起吧？

MAIN.original: Call me, Niko. We should go out on another date. I really want to find out more about you. xx
MAIN.translated: 给我打电话，Niko。我们应该再出去约次会。我真的很想深入了解你。xx

MAIN.original: We should go on another date, Niko. I'd love to hear about you and your life. xx
MAIN.translated: 我们应该再出去约次会，Niko。我很想了解一下你和你的人生。xx

MAIN.original: Gimme a call, Niko. I'd like to hear what you're up to. You can be honest with me, you know. xx
MAIN.translated: 给我打电话，Niko。我很想知道你在干什么。你可以坦诚对我，真的。xx

MAIN.original: Niko, man, call me for some work and ting. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: Niko，兄弟，要接活，打给我。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: You ignored my calls, breda. I and I needed to be taken home from hospital. Badman came pick me up instead. - Jacob
MAIN.translated: 你无视了我的电话，兄弟。当时我需要有人来医院接我回家。最后是Badman过来接的我。 - Jacob

MAIN.original: Cha! I still vexed about that dogheart Dimitri. You got them rude driving skills to get I and I away from there! Keep ya head down and keep in touch. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: 操！我还是很生那个狼心狗肺的Dimitri的气。能把咱俩从那儿弄出来，你的车技真是够牛！低调行事，保持联络。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: Irie star! You got crazy flying skills. I and I should fly over to Jamrock one day, sight? Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: 赞诶老兄！你丫的飞行技术牛逼啊。要么改天咱俩飞趟牙买加吧？就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: Niko, man. You left I. I hope there ain't nothing wrong and ting. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: Niko，兄弟。你丢下了我。希望你没遇上什么坏事。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: What goin' on, Niko? I cotching with Real Badman. He a hortical Don. Come see I. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: 近况如何，Niko？我现在和Real Badman在一起。他是实打实的大佬。来找我。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: Rhaatid, Niko. Be strong, sight? I going to find this bumbaclot! You need fe get some hardcore weapons and ting while you waiting for me call. I ain't got my car or I'd bring them to you. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: 妈的，Niko。坚强点，好吗？我会找到这个混账的！你先去整点重武器啥的，我到时候给你打电话。要不是我没车，我就直接把他们送到你面前了。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: Niko, give I a call if you need some cash. I and Badman usually got some jobs. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: Niko，你要是需要钱就打给我。我和Badman这儿一般都有活可干。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: I got an escape plan for you, star. Keep your eyes on the sky, sight?
MAIN.translated: 我准备好撤退方案了，老兄。注意着点天上，好吗？

MAIN.original: Niko star - you done real good for I and I, but there be too much Babylon boderation inna de place. Me and Badman ain't delivering no more packages, sight. Hope you liked dat Huntley in dem mean colors. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: Niko 兄弟，我们的活你完成得很好，但现在盯着那边的条子太多了。我和Badman不会再去送货了。希望你喜欢那辆成色不太好的Huntley。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: Niko. Whappening, man? Hit I up if ya need any weaponry. I got a car rammed with the shit. I drive it round to ya. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: Niko，怎么了，兄弟？缺装备了给我打个电话，我车里有的是这种东西。直接给你开过来。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: I and I is sick of selling these weapons to blood clots. Hit I up if you need I to bring you some. Easy - LJ
MAIN.translated: 我不想再把武器卖给那些逼玩意儿了。你有需要就给我打个电话。就这样 - LJ

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~No way bitch! We don't want you in here!
~z~~x~I don't think so - you're not welcome in Perseus.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~不许进来，神之子服饰不欢迎你。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Hiya, welcome to the world of Perseus.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你好啊，欢迎来到神之子的世界。
~z~~x~您好，神之子服饰感谢您的光顾。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Welcome to Perseus, I'll be your assistant today.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~欢迎光临神之子，我是您的导购。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You need to leave bitch - right now!
~z~~x~You're a maniac! Get the hell outta here!
~z~~x~Excellent choice, if you don't mind me saying?
~z~~x~You're gonna break some hearts in that...
~z~~x~That really suits you, brings out your eyes.
~z~~x~There's a man who knows what he wants.
~z~~x~Calm down, or I'll have to ask you to leave.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~注意点，不然就只能请您出去了。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~This isn't a playground sweetie, grow up, or get out.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这里不是游乐场，宝贝。不听话就滚蛋。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Listen sweetie, stop tittying about and buy something!
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~听着宝贝，要买就买，不买滚蛋！

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Honey, you're treading a very thin line!
~z~~x~Get a grip already, you're not in Binko now!
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~自制一点，这里不是杂牌服装店！

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Are you crazy? Don't pull that out here!
~z~~x~Put that shit away before I call the cops!
~z~~x~Nice, that's gonna get you noticed bro...
~z~~x~Alright, I bet you're gonna rock that look bro.
~z~~x~Good choice bro, got the same thing at home myself.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~好眼力啊，兄弟，这款我也有一套。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Nice, the ladies are gonna respond, trust me.
~z~~x~Listen bro, you damage it, you're payin' for it.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~听着兄弟，你弄坏的，你负责赔。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I did Wing Chun buddy, I'll kick your ass!
~z~~x~Oh yeah? This is LC baby, I've seen some shit, bring it!
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~咋了？这可是自由城，小子，爷啥没见过，来啊！

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Hey, you need any help, just holler, name's Mike.
~z~~x~Whoa, what the fuck? You don't need that bro!
~z~~x~Listen, I just work here, you can take what you like.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~听着，我就一打工的，店里东西随你拿。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Whoa, dude, were you in a Binco explosion or something?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~哇，老哥，你是刚从卖抹布的地方出来吗？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Bro, seriously, you're dressed like my dad dude.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~兄弟，说实话，你这穿的跟我爸似的。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Dude, no offence, but did you walk here from Alderney or something?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~老哥，有一说一，你这是刚从隔壁Alderney大乡村过来的吗？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Buddy, I think we've got just what you're after.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~伙计，我们这儿应该有你要的款式。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Ok, thinking of a new look huh?
~z~~x~Bro, you're in the right place, we can really help you out.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~兄弟，你这是来对店了，找我们准没错。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Nah, no way, I told you the last time.
~z~~x~You better split before I call LCPD.
~z~~x~My hand is on the alarm, just give me a reason.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我已经准备好报警了，你别乱来。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Bro, this ain't a Binco, tone it down.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~兄弟，这里不是垃圾店，注意点。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Buddy, I will throw your ass in the street, no problem.
~z~~x~Take the stick, Nicky. I'm gonna take the ladies.
~z~~x~Yo, Nicky. You're flying this sucker. Me and the chicks will sit back and look good.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~哟，Nicky。这玩意你来飞。我和姑娘们就坐后面看着。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Drive the chopper for us, NB. Okay?
~z~~x~Use your mad red army flying skills on the chopper, NB. I'm gonna use my hard abs to impress these girls.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~用你的牛逼红军飞行技术开直升机，NB。我要用我的钢铁腹肌征服这些妹子。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Can you drive the chopper for us? You're a fucking winner, Nicky. Don't forget that, bro.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~能麻烦你替我们开直升机吗？你丫可是赢家啊，Nicky，这可别忘了，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~The ladies and I are gonna need our hands. You fly the chopper, homie.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~姑娘和我都腾不出手。飞机你开，哥们儿。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Take us over to Broker Bridge. That thing is almost as cut as my delts.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~带大家去看Broker大桥。那玩意跟我的三角肌一样棱角分明。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Ladies, you see the bridge. You see Brucie. I know which you prefer. Let's head back, man.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~女士们，看看那桥，再看看Brucie。我知道你们会选哪个。回去吧，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Nicky man, let's hit up the Civic Citadel.
~z~~x~If I wasn't a sculpted as I am then I might even think you were competition. Let's go back, bro.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~要不是我身材这么好，说不定就把你当我的对手了。回去吧，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~How about we show these ladies Dragon Heart Plaza from the air, bro?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这次就让她们从空中见识下龙心广场吧，兄弟？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~This is the life, ain't it girls? Flying over the city with a pair of rock hard studs.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这才是生活啊，姑娘。与两匹铁打的骏马在城市上空飞翔。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Something to tell your grandkids, man. You should go back, homie.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~都可以讲给孙子孙女听了。该回去了，哥们儿。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You can't pay for a view like that.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这种风景花钱都没地方看的。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I mean if you could, I'd be able to afford it anyway! Let's head back, Nicky.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~就算真有地方看，我也掏得起那钱！该回去了，Nicky。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I'm feeling religious vibes here, NB. We should pass over the Columbus Cathedral.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我有点想去宗教圣地，NB。我们去哥伦布大教堂吧。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Shit, I feel almost as spiritual as I do after a big work out. Head back, NB.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~操，感觉自己得到了升华，跟猛力锻炼过一样。回去吧，NB。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Yo, go over to the Triangle Building, Nicky. There's some mad shit to show these girls around there.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~哟，去三角大楼那边吧，Nicky。那里有点牛逼玩意给姑娘们看。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~This is how it is when you roll with the big boys, hitting it hard. Let's go back, Nicky.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~和纯爷们在一起就是这种感觉，超稳健。可以回去了，Nicky。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Why don't we go to the Get a Life Building, NB?
~z~~x~Buzz the tower. Show them what life really is like for those who know how.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~全速前进。让她们见识下有品味的生活方式。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Man, we're winners. Do you know anyone like us, girls? C'mon, we're fucking beautiful. Head back, Nicky.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~天，我们是人生赢家。没见过我们这样的吧，姑娘们？真的，我们是一流的。回去吧，Nicky。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Head over to that standing erection, homie. Let these ladies check out the length of it.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~去看那个一柱擎天，哥们儿。让姑娘们见识下它的长度。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~It's fucking beautiful, man. I love that shit. If I was that big chimp I'd climb it too.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~太鸡巴漂亮了，兄弟。爱死它了。我是猩猩我也会爬上去的*。~n~(指电影中金刚爬上当时纽约最高楼的帝国大厦)

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~My arms aren't probably as big as his but fuck it. Hey, head back, Niko.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~虽说我的四肢没它那么发达，不过都无所谓。嘿，调头，Niko。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Take this thing down a little bit, homie. We want a good view.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~高度降低一些，哥们儿。找个好点的视角。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Take it down for a better look, NB.
~z~~x~Lower, Nicky. These girls want a better view.
~z~~x~We need to be higher for the sweet view, bro.
~z~~x~These girls want a good view, NB. Get the chopper up a bit.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~姑娘们嫌视角不好，NB。稍微拉高点。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Give us some altitude, Nicky. The ladies want to see this thing.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~往上走，Nicky。女士们想看的清楚些。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Brucie may be perfect, but he can't fly. Easy there, bro!
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~Brucie是很完美，但他不会飞啊。当心点，兄弟！

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Don't go crashing this shit, Nicky. It ain't cheap. Nothing about Brucie is cheap.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~别把飞机撞烂啊，Nicky。很贵的。Brucie的东西就没有便宜的。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Calm it, Nicky. It'd be tragic if people as hot as us died in a crash, stupid.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~当心，Nicky。咱俩这样的猛男坠机身亡可是个大悲剧，超蠢。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You're a real gentleman, Nicky. Big love, baby.
~z~~x~That was a wild ride, Nicky. Not as wild as the ride you girls are gonna get later, but, yeah - thanks man.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这段旅途实在是爽啊，Nicky。不过两位女士待会儿的经历会更爽。谢了兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Nicky, you work that thing like a fucking professional, alright? You're a winner just like me, bro.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~Nicky，你丫开直升机也太熟练了吧？你也是我这样的人生赢家，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You ain't seen nothing like that, have you girls, have you? That's how we roll baby. Always pushing it to the limit.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~从来没见过吧，姑娘们，没见过吧？这就是我们的风范，宝贝。向着极限前进。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~These girls were impressed, Nicky. They don't know that we roll like this everyday. We're winners, man.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~俩姑娘这下终身难忘了，Nicky。她们不知道这是我们的日常生活。我们是赢家啊，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~That's it ladies. The show is over. All you get to look at is Brucie's body. Lucky you.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~就到这里了，姑娘们。演出结束了。现在只需要看着Brucie的身体就行了，你们真走运。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Shit, homie. I'm starting to get bored of this chopper shit.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~操，哥们儿。直升机这玩意我都快乘腻了。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~It costs a lot but no one can tell you're spending the money because you're way up in the fucking sky. You know what I mean?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~直升机超烧钱，但你在天上飞，别人不知道你在烧钱。能明白我的意思吗？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Why don't us players show the girls how we roll? Go check out the Zirconium building.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~向姑娘们展示下我们两个大赢家的风范吧！去看看Zirconium大厦。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Hussle baby, Brucie don't wait for no man!
~z~~x~Me and Nicky are the tightest motherfuckers in the city. That's a fact. Cruise back now, homie.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我和Nicky是这座城市最铁的两兄弟，事实如此。返航吧，哥们儿。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Let's hit up the driving range, Nicky.
~z~~x~We can laugh at those silver medallists who don't have the cabbage to buy boats. Ha ha haaa!
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~还能好好笑话笑话那些买不起船的万年老二。哈哈！

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I could hit a ball harder than any of them, check out these triceps. Head back, Nicky.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我随手来一球都比他们猛，三头肌不是白练的。调头，Nicky。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Maybe we should show these ladies some industrial shit. Make it so, Nicky.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~给她们展示些工业风格吧。听我的，Nicky。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Impressive shit, right? Not as impressive as the steel I got in these calves, but cool. Go back now, Nicky.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~很壮观吧？比起我小腿的肌肉还是差了些，不过没事。回去吧，Nicky。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Let's show these girls those crazy rusted up ships, Nicky. Industrial decline, man.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~带姑娘们看看那些超炫的铁锈沉船吧，Nicky。工业衰退啊，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~The exact opposite of me - yeah, scientific progress.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~跟我完全相反，我是科学进步。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~you got to know I think things should be kept in perfect condition. Head back, Niko.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你们一定明白保持完美状态有多重要了。调头，Niko。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Easy, Nicky. I don't want to get these clothes wet, man.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~放松，Nicky。我可不想把衣服弄湿，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Come on, homie. The ladies and I don't want to swim.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~别这样，哥们儿。我和姑娘们没考虑游泳。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~This is an expensive paint job, NB. Not that I give a shit about money. I got shitloads of it.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~这船涂装很贵的，NB。不是说我出不起那钱，要钱我有的是。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~I like my boat to look as good as my body. Watch the paintwork, homie.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我希望船能和我的肉体一样完美。别刮花了，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Nicky, the ladies and me are real grateful, brother.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~Nicky，我和姑娘们都很感谢你，兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Nicely done, Nicky. You are a winner, just like Brucie. Ain't that right, ladies?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~真是出色，Nicky。你就是赢家，跟Brucie一样。我没说错吧，女士们？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You can captain my boat any day, I'd let you captain these ladies but they want the Brucie.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你随时都可以来上我的船，其实几位女士也可以上，不过她们只想要Brucie。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~NB, you must have learned that shit in the red army. Mad crazy. We all love you, bro.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~NB，你是在红军学的开船吧。太牛逼了。我们爱死你了，Niko。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Thanks for being the pilot, Nicky. I would have let these chicks thank you but I got plans for them. Yeah!
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~感谢你替我开船，Nicky。我是想让她俩好好谢谢你，不过她们我早有安排。耶！

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Ice cold Nicky, you're a fucking prince. He's a prince, ain't he ladies? Ain't he?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~冷面无情Nicky，你丫就是个亲王。他就是亲王，你说呢，姑娘们？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You wanna be captain, Nicky? I want to give these women all my attention.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~船长就你当吧，Nicky？我想全身心投入到两位女士身上。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You're taking charge of the ship, Nicky. I'm taking charge of these ladies.
~z~~x~You're the captain, Nicky. Me and these hot chicks are the crew.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你是船长，Nicky。我跟这两个辣妹只是船员。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Homie, you're going to have to drive. I need both my hands free to handle these chicks.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~哥们儿，船只能你来开。我的两只手都要用来把妹。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Nicky, I need you to drive the boat. That cool?
~z~~x~Take us over to the Statue of Happiness. That's some intense shit.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~带大家去看幸福女神像*，那玩意老牛逼了。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You ladies are much hotter than that bitch. Let's cruise back, Nicky.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你们二位比那尊鬼神性感多了。我们返航吧，Nicky。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Let's show these ladies some romantic shit. Prove that us alphas got a sensitive side too.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~今天带两位女士看点浪漫的。让她们知道我们猛男也有感性的一面。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~You girls can't even concentrate on this shit. You're thinking about my pecs, right. Let's go back, Nicky.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~你们二位根本没心思参观吧。满脑子都是我的胸肌，对不对？我们回去吧，Nicky。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Cruise over to Pier 45, Nicky. We ride in style.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~向45号码头进发，Nicky。我们霸气出航。

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~Nicky, man. We're fucking winners. We don't wanna get labelled as sailors or something, ok?
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~Nicky，兄弟。我们就是牛逼赢家。我们可不想被人当作什么傻逼水手，OK？

MAIN.original: ~z~~x~We're animals, we need to hunt on dry land. I'm done with this boating shit.
MAIN.translated: ~z~~x~我们是猛兽，我们要在陆地上狩猎。开船的事暂时就到这儿了。

MAIN.original: ~z~Righteous, bredren. Good fe see de I.
~z~Wagwan Niko? Good fe see de man.
~z~Yeah man, me have di heavy firepower ya need, ya know man.
MAIN.translated: ~z~是的，兄弟，我有你要的重火力，懂吧。

MAIN.original: ~z~All de heat is right here, seen?
~z~I got some teeth inna here ya know, bredren.
~z~Everyting a mafia don could want innna dis shit.
MAIN.translated: ~z~混黑帮的需要的东西我全都有。

MAIN.original: ~z~Yeah man, check this shit out ma bredren.
MAIN.translated: ~z~是的，兄弟，你尽管挑吧，好兄弟。

MAIN.original: ~z~I an' I got nuff guns ya know, my youth.
~z~Ya been blacking up too much me breda?
~z~Niko, ya need fe calm yourself down.
~z~Cha, Niko. What kind of fuckery's a go on?
~z~Cha, me need fe get outta here me bredren, later.
MAIN.translated: ~z~擦，我要先离开这儿了，好兄弟，回见。

MAIN.original: ~z~I hot stepping outa here Niko. See ya.
~z~I and I best clear outta here before Babylon arrive.
MAIN.translated: ~z~我最好在条子来之前赶紧跑路。

MAIN.original: ~z~Yo, I and I should be geting outta here bredren.
~z~Yo, dis rasta be getting outta here. Later.
MAIN.translated: ~z~哟，老兄我要先走一步了。回见。

MAIN.original: ~z~One love, Niko. I and I be seeing each other real soon.
~z~Later my youth. Call me and ting.
~z~Keep outta trouble bredren. I and I see ya soon.
MAIN.translated: ~z~祝你平平安安，兄弟。日后再见。
